{"tid":1248982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［啱聽就推］各位睇尾班車做人啊！通宵留守百害而無一利！","createTime":"2019-06-21T15:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T16:36:49.000Z","uid":70403,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e75ae8bc2bbad83cb893fae169fc455427131806","tid":1248982,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">趁尾班車個段時間慢慢散走！<br />\n唔好俾機會班警犬坐尾班車返屋企！<br />\n班狗咁撚串，坐警車返屋企啦！</div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>今日社運一大躍進，證明遊擊圍堵係可行！<br />\n<br />\n出面嘅香港手足要好好保護自己！！<br />\n<br />\n眼看四方，睇下會唔會有警車調派過嚟想包抄！<br />\n<br />\n見到有唔對路要即刻大喊通知現場香港人！<br />\n<br />\n唔好怕尷尬，出得嚟就係真正香港人！<br />\n<br />\n反抗係長期作戰！唔係一日就搞掂！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">務必要考慮離場時間，方向位置！<br />\n<br />\n入夜後，警犬就會變人狼！小心！<br />\n<br />\n一定一定要查清楚尾班車係幾時！<br />\n<br />\n見到記者都開始少就要準備定退！<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，你冇義務要留守通宵！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你今日肯出嚟已經好好！<br />\n<br />\n不定期遊擊圍堵行動已開始！</span></span></div><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>留得青山在，哪怕無柴燒！</strong>"},{"pid":"1e8a5137ab465751fba1c9357cba916a825e57e6","tid":1248982,"uid":62837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"準備明天返工！"},{"pid":"aa38de4328d372f2cb6f02e4ec034fa0b67260b1","tid":1248982,"uid":70403,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>我個藍絲老豆罕有地認同今次圍警總行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油香港人，終於搵到和理真玩法！</strong>"},{"pid":"41e09bcfebd49480917d1def029f28241fbbaf01","tid":1248982,"uid":47924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f06201cc4092b0cefa3ca05e743847cfba8f0db","tid":1248982